title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VIII - Lisbon updated
description:
Earlier this week World Update VIII has been released which has the focus on Portugal and Spain. Based on one of my followers feedback I found out that WU 8 was only partially (although the marketplace showed it as installed). After reinstalling the WU I indeed have more POI's including the bridges I was missing in the previous video. Based on this I decided to create a new video now with all POI's included.
